STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
R.K., Defendant-Petitioner. C-861 September Term 2017
080561 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003540-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
